Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 30000 THEN '<$30,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 60000 THEN '$30,000 - $60,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 90000 THEN '$60,000 - $90,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" < 120000 THEN '$90,000 - $120,000' WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Dim_W_HOUSEHOLD_D"."HH_INCOME" >= 120000 THEN '>$120,000' ELSE 'Unspecified' END
